其實點偷渡到去台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼要行多3日3夜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:14:27.000Z","msg":"出面應該有駁船<br />\n你估次次大飛過大海咩"},{"pid":"04f1cedb54885a5a719a081115c02717441c289e","tid":2176920,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"其實正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"04125b431c8e5ea17a0695f278c9feb056218d39","tid":2176920,"uid":337052,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"254a71da95bd4fe0440a2c0bc4c599c49e9f400e","tid":2176920,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:13:56.000Z","msg":"架船連公海都未出<br />\n其實點偷渡到去台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼要行多3日3夜"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:16:04.000Z","msg":"普通漁船約36小時<br />\n洗頭艇約18小時"},{"pid":"9f8e11ecefba80d8cec56ee1c0b56b23cb495611","tid":2176920,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"04f1cedb54885a5a719a081115c02717441c289e","tid":2176920,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"其實正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:16:34.000Z","msg":"能做不能說"},{"pid":"183d79b264b30f8ad2c1eeae3778917764ad1103","tid":2176920,"uid":273703,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:17:23.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"221a35a77939a5fe73a434e194bba465f5f0fe5c","tid":2176920,"uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":2,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"bf07eb73c816f857724a9cdc0c21f9b4ca75ae87","tid":2176920,"uid":34869,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"254a71da95bd4fe0440a2c0bc4c599c49e9f400e","tid":2176920,"uid":273218,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":2,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:13:56.000Z","msg":"架船連公海都未出<br />\n其實點偷渡到去台灣<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/wonder.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n起碼要行多3日3夜"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:14:27.000Z","msg":"出面應該有駁船<br />\n你估次次大飛過大海咩"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:17:27.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn2.ettoday.net/images/3447/d3447885.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn2.ettoday.net%2Fimages%2F3447%2Fd3447885.jpg&h=43b1ec48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n可以先去東沙島"},{"pid":"11f86a2743e4d8081d467ed13accf56641c5d9b3","tid":2176920,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:18:43.000Z","msg":"唔係你肯唔肯收<br />\n係匪徒肯唔肯放人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"12abdda04870d0060785eb329e5ef039cf1f606e","tid":2176920,"uid":305349,"like":10,"dislike":0,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:19:53.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/biggrin.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2f7cf635db196dfeaee518f7e267c5dce9604825","tid":2176920,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:22:02.000Z","msg":"財團法人臺港經濟文化合作策進會<br />\n<br />\n策進會<span class=\"red\">「臺港服務交流辦公室」</span>7月1日正式營運提供服務(2020-07-01)<br />\n    財團法人臺港經濟文化合作策進會（簡稱策進會）今（1）日表示，依據策進會促進臺港交流與互動之宗旨，特成立「臺港服務交流辦公室」，下設「諮詢服務」、「專案管理」及「行政庶務」3分組，以提升對港人之協助與服務。<br />\n    策進會指出，該專案辦公室提供港人來臺就學、就業、投資創業、移民定居等專案諮詢與協處服務，除設置<span class=\"red\">2支諮詢專線（02-2700-3199、02-2397-1088）</span>，於周一至周五(例假日除外)上午9時至12時、下午1時30分至5時由專人接聽，並提供專屬電子信箱<span class=\"red\">careyou@thec.org.tw</span>，讓諮詢管道更多元、暢通。<br />\n    策進會表示，該會網站已開設專區，彙整諮詢常見Q&amp;A等相關資料庫資訊，以便利各界查詢；並建立相關機關聯繫窗口，依據既有法律規範及公私協力方式，務實處理港人關懷服務事項。"},{"pid":"1c7572a97c9c2cfe4d1ada30c2bbdb36ad0af32d","tid":2176920,"uid":286155,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:22:10.000Z","msg":"即係直接送中"},{"pid":"c52f998ec1d886794f2c23952ed619e1833c8434","tid":2176920,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"11f86a2743e4d8081d467ed13accf56641c5d9b3","tid":2176920,"uid":254594,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:18:43.000Z","msg":"唔係你肯唔肯收<br />\n係匪徒肯唔肯放人<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:22:29.000Z","msg":"可惡的共匪"},{"pid":"badee77da4e014d6ba10a1535aa0601907b99865","tid":2176920,"uid":337052,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:25:30.000Z","msg":"財團法人臺港經濟文化合作策進會<br />\n<a href=\"http://www.thec.org.tw/Default.asp\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fwww.thec.org.tw%2FDefault.asp&d=a8feNXbjtso6d%2BC97Zvpkz4xCSFqVWWaKp6LAuIW5iI%3D&h=7d31dea5\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">http://www.thec.org.tw/Default.asp</a>"},{"pid":"28a5dbfba5433f70364647b43cfbf6ce61689e87","tid":2176920,"uid":222970,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:28:16.000Z","msg":"不鼓勵 但佢冇話強烈反對 相信大家都知咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n算係咁啦台灣政府已經好好"},{"pid":"e51c11582302ad2298c39ddfee43311a02f22b70","tid":2176920,"uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"28a5dbfba5433f70364647b43cfbf6ce61689e87","tid":2176920,"uid":222970,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:28:16.000Z","msg":"不鼓勵 但佢冇話強烈反對 相信大家都知咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n算係咁啦台灣政府已經好好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:30:49.000Z","msg":"台灣政府從來沒有遣返香港人"},{"pid":"f2352d7b64b58a413aa2aaf4d9a6a1a52a5fb87e","tid":2176920,"uid":16057,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"e51c11582302ad2298c39ddfee43311a02f22b70","tid":2176920,"uid":337052,"like":4,"dislike":0,"score":4,"quote":{"pid":"28a5dbfba5433f70364647b43cfbf6ce61689e87","tid":2176920,"uid":222970,"like":5,"dislike":0,"score":5,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:28:16.000Z","msg":"不鼓勵 但佢冇話強烈反對 相信大家都知咩意思<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/adore.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n算係咁啦台灣政府已經好好"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:30:49.000Z","msg":"台灣政府從來沒有遣返香港人"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:32:11.000Z","msg":"所以台灣政府這樣處理算是對香港人很好了"},{"pid":"edc58c9b410908a53f0e31f2a8169154c39af983","tid":2176920,"uid":337052,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:36:50.000Z","msg":"台港服務交流辦公室提供港人到台就學、就業、投資創業、移民定居，以及跨國企業、國際法人團體到台等專案諮詢與協助服務；同時也會在兼顧國家安全前提下，依據既有法律規範及公私協力方式，務實處理港人人道援助事宜。<br />\n<br />\n港人若因政治因素而致安全及自由受有緊急危害，即《港澳條例》第18條規定情形，只要與「台港服務交流辦公室」聯繫，辦公室即啟動「援助關懷專案」，專人協助基本生活照顧，輔導在台就學、就業。"},{"pid":"9703c250e66600ec69e88d323a3ea3ba8735d3cb","tid":2176920,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f8e11ecefba80d8cec56ee1c0b56b23cb495611","tid":2176920,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"04f1cedb54885a5a719a081115c02717441c289e","tid":2176920,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"其實正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:16:34.000Z","msg":"能做不能說"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:01:32.000Z","msg":"對外咁講姐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"2dd5bfe4fd0e874f61e20b5a9c395fc93a40b416","tid":2176920,"uid":279357,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:04:21.000Z","msg":"呢啲無鬼點死人<br />\n坐快艇咪出事羅"},{"pid":"3d71b8ffac90c1d7b29f9cd8d2826e34fef1be7e","tid":2176920,"uid":79410,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"quote":{"pid":"9703c250e66600ec69e88d323a3ea3ba8735d3cb","tid":2176920,"uid":5490,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"quote":{"pid":"9f8e11ecefba80d8cec56ee1c0b56b23cb495611","tid":2176920,"uid":337052,"like":3,"dislike":0,"score":3,"quote":{"pid":"04f1cedb54885a5a719a081115c02717441c289e","tid":2176920,"uid":21545,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:14:52.000Z","msg":"其實正常<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T11:16:34.000Z","msg":"能做不能說"},"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2020-08-27T12:01:32.000Z","msg":"對外咁講姐<img src=\"/